---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import CTA from "../components/CTA.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="GTM Vector - Outbound GTM Architecture"
  description="From ICP definition to tooling and workflows, we design outbound systems teams can actually run."
>
  <main class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-8 py-16">
    <section class="pt-6">
      <h1 class="text-5xl font-bold tracking-tight">
        Outbound GTM architecture built to scale.
      </h1>
      <p class="text-lg opacity-80 mt-6 max-w-3xl leading-7">
        GTM Vector helps B2B teams turn outbound into a repeatable system:
        targeting rules, data workflows, deliverability, tooling, and an operating model your team can run.
      </p>

      <div class="mt-10">
        <CTA />
      </div>

      <div class="mt-10 flex flex-wrap gap-3 text-sm opacity-80">
        <span class="rounded-full border border-white/10 bg-white/5 px-3 py-1">ICP rules</span>
        <span class="rounded-full border border-white/10 bg-white/5 px-3 py-1">Deliverability</span>
        <span class="rounded-full border border-white/10 bg-white/5 px-3 py-1">Clay / Apollo</span>
        <span class="rounded-full border border-white/10 bg-white/5 px-3 py-1">Instantly</span>
        <span class="rounded-full border border-white/10 bg-white/5 px-3 py-1">HubSpot</span>
        <span class="rounded-full border border-white/10 bg-white/5 px-3 py-1">n8n</span>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="mt-16">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">Start here</h2>
      <p class="opacity-80 mt-3 max-w-3xl">
        These are the highest-intent pages. If you’re already running outbound, one of these will likely be your bottleneck.
      </p>

      <div class="mt-8 grid gap-4 sm:grid-cols-2">
        <a class="rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-white/5 p-6 hover:bg-white/10 transition" href="/outbound-automation/">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold">Outbound Automation</h3>
          <p class="opacity-80 mt-2">ICP rules, list building, segmentation, sequences, routing, monitoring.</p>
        </a>

        <a class="rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-white/5 p-6 hover:bg-white/10 transition" href="/cold-email-deliverability/">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold">Cold Email Deliverability</h3>
          <p class="opacity-80 mt-2">Domain setup, inbox placement, warming, and safe sending patterns.</p>
        </a>

        <a class="rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-white/5 p-6 hover:bg-white/10 transition" href="/ai-sdr/">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold">AI SDR</h3>
          <p class="opacity-80 mt-2">Use AI upstream without frying deliverability or sounding like a bot.</p>
        </a>

        <a class="rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-white/5 p-6 hover:bg-white/10 transition" href="/compare/">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold">Compare</h3>
          <p class="opacity-80 mt-2">High-intent pages that rank and convert.</p>
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="mt-16">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">What you get</h2>

      <div class="mt-8 grid gap-4 sm:grid-cols-2">
        <div class="rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-white/5 p-6">
          <h3 class="font-semibold">A working outbound system</h3>
          <p class="opacity-80 mt-2">Targeting rules, enrichment, segmentation, sequences, and QA checks.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-white/5 p-6">
          <h3 class="font-semibold">Docs + handover</h3>
          <p class="opacity-80 mt-2">Playbooks, templates, and a weekly operating cadence your team follows.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-white/5 p-6">
          <h3 class="font-semibold">Stack integration</h3>
          <p class="opacity-80 mt-2">We plug into what you already use: Apollo, Clay, Instantly, HubSpot, n8n.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-white/5 p-6">
          <h3 class="font-semibold">Meetings as the KPI</h3>
          <p class="opacity-80 mt-2">We optimize for booked calls, not vanity metrics.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-14">
        <CTA headline="Want a quick teardown?" subhead="Send your current setup and I’ll tell you the top 3 fixes to improve meetings fast." />
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</Layout>
